sql:
SELECT location_id, AVG(temperature) AS average_temperature
FROM environmental_readings
WHERE location_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
January 2023 refers to the period from '2023-01-01' to '2023-01-31'; 
Environmental readings include temperature and humidity measurements; 
Alerts and errors refer to any issues or anomalies detected during the readings.

